com.atakmap.android.maps

Class MapEventDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.maps.MapEventDispatcher

  • public class MapEventDispatcher
extends java.lang.Object
    Central dispatch point for MapEvents. The MapView encapsulates an instance of MapEventDispatcher available through MapView.getMapEventDispatcher().
